title: ***Spacious Layouts With Panoramic Views - Open Weekends For Tour ***
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Concrete construction creates acoustically sound units', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
